Randall is a proven leader with over twenty-six years experience in the chemical industry. Dearth have managed teams responsible for marketing, R&D, manufacturing, finance, law, HR, IT, PR and procurement. In 2004, Randall was part of the leadership team that developed and implemented the corporate organization for LANXESS after Bayer split out their chemicals business into this new, independent legal entity.
In 2012 Dearth became the President and CEO of Calgon Carbon Corporation- a leader in water and air purification technology.



